Interface ValueTypeAssertion<V>

  • Type Parameters:
    V - the type of the topic values
    All Superinterfaces:

    All Known Implementing Classes:

    public interface ValueTypeAssertion<V>
extends NamedCollection.Option
    Defines a NamedCollection.Option for asserting the type of values used with a NamedTopic.

      • withRawTypes

        @Default
static <V> ValueTypeAssertion<V> withRawTypes()
        Obtains a ValueTypeAssertion that allows topic to be acquired and assigned to a raw NamedTopic reference. A debug log message will be raised for topics that have been configured with specific types.
        Returns:
        a ValueTypeAssertion
